00:02:19.444 --> 00:02:23.069
Because of that, we can put the Containers in

00:02:23.069 --> 00:02:27.305
our Environment where they can be deployed to all of the students at the same time.

00:02:27.305 --> 00:02:31.040
We can control authorization to them in the same way.

00:02:31.039 --> 00:02:33.109
Just like with the Shipping Containers,

00:02:33.110 --> 00:02:39.190
